Package: txtools
Title: An interface betwen GenomicAlignments and transcriptomic representations
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Miguel Angel",
           family = "Garcia-Campos",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "angel.campos@weizmann.ac.il",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5223-8174", 
                       webpage = "https://angelcampos.github.io/"))
Description: txtools extends the functionality of GenomicAlignments filtering 
    and processing RNA-seq reads aligned to a genome into their transcriptomic
    versions and allows data to be represented in a transcriptomic oriented way.
